{
  "texts": [
    "The results of the same query/prompt may vary across multiple trials and the models underlying the app can be updated at any time.",
    "This implies that there is a certain randomness to the evaluation and analysis of the translations.",
    "Furthermore, currently, a novel LLM (GPT-4) has been developed and can be accessed through a $20 monthly subscription to ChatGPT.",
    "According to Jiao et al. (2023), GPT-4 outperforms GPT-3.5 as an MT system which warrants for a replication using GPT-4.",
    "Nevertheless, the free version of ChatGPT is still based on GPT-3.5, implying that a large amount of users will still be using the currently investigated model for their daily needs."
  ]
}